line_1: Witness the Mighty Bastions of Namure.
line_2: What cou'd they not Perform, or what Endure?

line_1: The gladded Monarch said,when at Namure,
line_2: Ramsay fell on and mock'd the Gallick Power,

line_1: The gladded Monarch said,when at Namure,
line_2: And emulating Nations wondring first gave o're.
